  "text": "No significant associations were found between the decline in the diagnosis transitional status and a decline in the scores of the MoCA and MMSE from baseline to 3-6 months. This could be due to spontaneous recovery in cognition (e.g., language) [CITATION_1] as a result of the short timeframe of 3-6 months between the two assessments.",
